  "text": "She may have had exposed mesh for years, and it was only discovered because of her urinary symptoms. 5. Other literature, albeit with shorter average follow-up, has not noted any association between these slings and malignancy [CITATION_1] . 6. Given the millions of women with these slings, it is inevitable some will develop malignancies, just as do some women without slings.",
